amespace。\n> 2. 在 `HomePage.initState`（或全局初始化逻辑）中建立连接并传入 `us
erId` query 参数。\n> 3. 监听 `match:created` 事件，将 payload 转换为 `MatchSumm
ary` 后 dispatch `ExternalMatchReceived(summary)` 到 `MatchingBloc`。\n\nI think
the simplest approach is:\n1. Add `userId` to `AuthAuthenticated` state\n2. Upda
te `AuthBloc` to pass `userId` from `UserResponse.id`\n3. In `HomePage`, use `Bl
ocListener<AuthBloc, AuthState>` or read the auth state to get userId\n4. Create
`MatchingSocketClient` \n5. Initialize socket when auth is authenticated\n\nActu
ally, let me think about the architecture. The `HomePage` is inside `MainPage` w
hich has `MultiBlocProvider` for `MatchingBloc` and `MatchListCubit`. The `AuthB
loc` is above `SocialWorldApp` in the widget tree.\n\nIn `HomePage`, I can use `
context.read<AuthBloc>().state` to get the auth state. If `AuthAuthenticated` ha
s `userId`, I can use it.\n\nLet me update `AuthAuthenticated` to include `userI
d`:\n```dart\nclass AuthAuthenticated extends AuthState {\n  final String userId
