sh 遇到 pre-push hook 失败，同样阅读错误、修复、重试\n\nThe golden test failures
are pre-existing and unrelated to my matching changes. They fail because golden 
files are environment-specific (different Flutter versions, screen resolutions, 
fonts, etc.). However, I can\'t just skip them.\n\nWait, let me re-read the inst
ructions more carefully:\n> 3. 修改完成后按项目技术栈运行自测（不要只跑 go test
