n>      cd apps/mobile && flutter pub get\n>      cd apps/mobile && flutter anal
yze\n>      cd apps/mobile && flutter test\n>    - 若修改了 Node/NestJS 后端代码
：\n>      cd apps/api && npm test\n>      cd apps/api && npm run build\n>    - 
通用检查：\n>      make check-docs（文档检查）\n\nThe instructions say to run `f
lutter test`, but the golden test failures are pre-existing. I should report thi
s honestly.\n\nHowever, the pre-push hook is blocking me. Let me check what `mak
e test` does and if I can make the golden tests pass.\n\nActually, looking at th
e golden test failures - they\'re all minor pixel differences (0.17%, 0.47%, 0.4
8%). This is typical for golden tests across different environments. I can updat
e the golden files by running `flutter test --update-goldens`.\n\nBut wait - upd
ating golden files would add binary image files to the commit, which might not b
